{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act12side", "eventName": "多索雷斯假日", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DH-3", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "拔銃相助", "storyInfo": "比賽逐漸白熱化，林雨霞發現了危險分子的蹤跡，她沒有進一步深入。\n另一邊，陳為了幫助名為水月的選手，在巷子中與人大打出手。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "距離比賽開始已經過去了半個多小時，而令人吃驚的是，居然還沒有一支獲得了赤金的隊伍選擇提前結束比賽。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來，這一次大獎賽的參賽選手們野心都非常的大！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "潘喬先生，您怎麼看？", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_192_1#7"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來今年的大獎賽會是非常激烈的一屆，我很期待。", "name": "潘喬"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_192_1#7"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_NPC_017_3"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯，想必所有觀眾都和潘喬先生是同樣的心情。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的各個分舞台將會持續進行對各個隊伍的追蹤，以保證觀眾們不會錯過任何一場精彩的戰鬥。", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而我們的觀眾也不要閒下來，讓我們將這份急迫的心情轉換成投票的動力，為心愛的選手投出寶貴的一票吧！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為他花錢，才是真的愛他！", "name": "D.D.D."}, "figure_art": "avg_NPC_017_3"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G02"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_202", "name2": "avg_npc_204", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "親愛的，救命！", "name": "懶散的女遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_202"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_202", "name2": "avg_npc_204"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別怕，寶寶，我這就來救你！", "name": "急躁的男遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_202"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.5, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_npc_204", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name2": "avg_npc_204"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_201", "name2": "avg_npc_204", "enter": "left", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_201", "name2": "avg_npc_204"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "jump", "xpos": 100.0, "power": 0.0, "times": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.1, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$fightgeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "jump", "power": 5.0, "times": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_201", "name2": "avg_npc_204", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，還以為這對情侶是來搞笑的，怎麼這麼能打？！", "name": "急躁的參賽選手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_204"}, {"id": 55, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_202", "name2": "avg_npc_201", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寶寶，太好了，我差點以為我要失去你了。 （小聲）你就不能自己想想辦法嗎？！", "name": "急躁的男遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_202", "name2": "avg_npc_201", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗚嗚嗚，他們好凶。 （小聲）*玻利瓦爾俚語*，我的人設可是弱女子！", "name": "懶散的女遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_202"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_202", "name2": "avg_npc_201", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，已經沒事了，看我狠狠教訓他們一頓！ （小聲）嘖，姑奶奶你也努努力好不好。", "name": "急躁的男遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_202", "name2": "avg_npc_201", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "親愛的，你是最棒的~ （小聲）你敢凶我？！", "name": "懶散的女遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_202"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（這兩個人，身手很不錯，而且有軍旅氣質，恐怕過去是軍人。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（至於情侶身份，恐怕是一種噱頭，用來博取觀眾好感。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（雖然很浮誇，不過不失為一種方法。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#4"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（雖然真的很浮誇。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#4"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（要是詩懷雅那個女人看到，大概會興沖沖地說她也想在這種比賽玩一玩這種角色扮演。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（......還是不要讓她知道比較好。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（總之，這對情侶穩贏，沒什麼好看的了，這裡搜了一圈也沒有赤金，該走了。）", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（二十塊赤金，恐怕有不少被放在了顯眼的位置，比如各種地標建築上，那些地方會很搶手。）", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（沒什麼必要去搶這些赤金。）", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（我應該去找那些剩下的被藏在隱蔽角落的赤金。）", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（不過......如果真的存在想透過比賽引發混亂的傢伙，他們至少肯定會尋找無人機和攝影機的死角再採取行動。）", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#4"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（兩邊都有做的必要......應該先和陳暉潔商量一下的，嘖，走得太急了。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#4"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（算了，我也不想和那個幼稚的女人商量，走一步看一步吧。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陳小姐，我可以問個問題嗎？", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你和林小姐原本是朋友吧？", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......為什麼你會這麼認為？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "因為要說你們是仇人的話，感覺沒有那麼尖銳。而要說你們只是有過節的話，你們又明顯挺瞭解對方的。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#5"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......算是吧。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "小的時候讀過同一所小學，而且有一個共同的熟人。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你猜得相當接近。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我不會告訴你我為什麼會和她關係不好。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事，像你們這樣的人，要是有過節肯定不是小事，我也不打算細問，只是找個話題罷了。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#6"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，你們看起來都沒想到對方會出現在這裡。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那不管怎麼說，也算是一種緣分，你有沒有考慮過和她重新搞好關係？", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你很關心這件事？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那倒不是......或者也是，這座城市裡一天到晚都是錢錢錢的，友情這種東西很奢侈的。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#2"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這不是我或者她想要搞好關係就能搞好關係的事。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，陳小姐，看那邊巷子裡。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_437_mizuki_1#4"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......有點麻煩。", "name": "水月"}, "figure_art": "avg_437_mizuki_1#4"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_437_mizuki_1#2"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "攝影機這麼多，萬一動起手來下手太重就不妙了欸。", "name": "水月"}, "figure_art": "avg_437_mizuki_1#2"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_205"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，不知道為什麼，老是打不中這小子，莫名其妙的。", "name": "急躁的參賽選手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_205"}, {"id": 139, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_204"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "居然敢耍我們，一起上！", "name": "憤怒的參賽選手"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_204"}, {"id": 141, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看樣子，是那個單人參賽的選手中了埋伏。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼說，陳小姐？等他們打完？", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你打算去幫他？", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這沒什麼好處，沒人會在大獎賽裡幫助別人，堂堂正正之類的想法在這裡是不適用的。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#3"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我知道。你在這裡等我一會就好。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#7", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "left", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#3", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "話音未落，陳已經衝了出去。"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1#7", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1#7"}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "埃內斯托沉默片刻，沒有跟上。"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6, "crossfade": 1.0}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（連這種角落都裝有攝影機，這應該不是只為了比賽而準備的了。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（不過，居民區的住宅裡應該還是沒有攝影機的，恐怕只有無人機拍攝到了有選手進入民宅才會進入跟拍。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（也就是說，只要沒被拍到進入民宅的舉動，不被官方發現的可能性就很高。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（利用這點的話......嗯？）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_205", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#7"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（......呵，說來就來。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#7"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#5", "name2": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "right", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.6, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_205", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_205", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣？", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1#5"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_205", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們這邊的炸彈安裝完成了，拉菲艾拉。", "name": "參賽選手？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_205"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_205", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好哦，我這邊也完成了。", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1#5"}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們去下一個地點吧。", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1#5"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_205", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，我剛才收到C隊的人求救，他們那邊好像遇到很難搞的對手了。", "name": "參賽選手？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_205"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_205", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是誰？", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1#2"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_205", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是那個鼠膽龍威隊裡的陳。", "name": "參賽選手？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_205"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_205", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哥哥說過，不要去觸高手的霉頭。", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1#1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從附近調一支隊伍過去，不要搞得太明顯，打不過就放棄，不要戀戰，正事要緊。", "name": "拉菲艾拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_421_laplum_1#1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_421_laplum_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_205", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "參賽選手？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_205"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetim": 1.5}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "ypos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "在拉菲艾拉和其他人離開後，林雨霞悄無聲息地從房樑上跳下，出現在他們剛才所站的位置。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#5", "fadetime": 0.2}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "ypos": 50.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "精於此道的她沒花多少功夫就找到了拉菲艾拉口中提到的炸彈。", "x": 300.0, "y": 370.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（......居然是來真的。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（想不到這個女孩居然是這些人其中的一員。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#5"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#4"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（他們說的正事恐怕是繼續安裝炸彈，聽起來他們有好幾支隊伍。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#4"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（雖然官方禁止了通訊設備，不過看來他們有自己的方法可以暗中取得聯繫。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#4"}, {"id": 248, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（還不知道對方有沒有後手，我現在繼續跟蹤他們恐怕意義也不大，而且有被發現的危險。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（而且，炸彈、哥哥、對我們有瞭解，有這幾個關鍵字應該足夠了。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（......會合的時間也差不多到了，正好去看看陳暉潔那邊吧。）", "name": "林雨霞"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_196_1#1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使沒有因為比賽而騰空，平日也十分冷清的巷子，此時卻格外的熱鬧。"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "20_I04", "xScale": 1.3, "yScale": 1.3, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"yTo": 50.0, "duration": 30.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "屋頂、窗台、陽台、圍牆上，不懷好意的參賽選手們冷冷地盯著站在巷子中央的陳。"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陳渾然不懼，只是緊了緊手裡的高壓水銃。"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "巷子口，剛剛得到陳救助的水月和埃內斯托站在一起，水月一臉驚喜，而埃內斯托則面帶猶豫。"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，此時已經沒有人去關注他們。"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沉默彌漫在巷子中，空氣彷彿也在此時凝固。"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯有帶著水氣的熱風吹起的髮梢證明著，此情此景並非一幅靜止畫。"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "20_I04", "xScale": 1.0, "yScale": 1.0, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“滴答”。"}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知何處，沒有關緊的水龍頭中滴下了一滴水，而水滴撞擊水槽帶來的細微聲響，卻如同一塊石頭砸入平靜的湖面。"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_soldiersrun"}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "霎時間，周圍的參賽選手一擁而上，陳也邁開了腳步。"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_196_1#1", "fadetim": 0.2}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "中途趕到的林雨霞在屋頂上冷靜地確認著周圍的情況。"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（陳暉潔這個女人，又在逞英雄。）", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（真是永遠學不乖，懶得幫她。）", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（不過，周圍有幾支隊伍聽到了動靜在往這邊趕。）", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（......擋一下吧，引起太多人注意沒有好處。）", "name": "林雨霞"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "林雨霞鬆了鬆手腕，從屋頂跳下，在巷子口落定。"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不遠處，已經出現了人影，她微微吐了一口氣，擺開了架勢。"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}